score\": 0.9927483490095098, \"rank\": 0.004464721107664419, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\"}, {\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darragh_Greene\", \"score\": 0.9999998038083696, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Darragh Greene\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darragh_Greene\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darragh_Greene\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9885334716888766, \"rank\": 0.011231188902856577, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland will have 12 swimmers in Paris in total and will also send two women's relay squads, as they compete in the the 4x100m medley and freestyle relays.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999828755791, \"rank\": 1.7041706267620738e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999457645037, \"rank\": 5.423552818462945e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's medley squad at the moment is Daniel Hill, Mona McSharry and Ellen Walshe, with the freestyle leg to be decided after the 4x100m freestyle relay.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_G._Hill\", \"score\": 0.9997663614430459, \"rank\": 0.0002336920421561026, \"text\": \"Daniel Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_G._Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_G._Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 554, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Walshe\", \"score\": 0.9999979159039302, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellen Walshe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Walshe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Walshe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That 4x100m team will comprise of Danielle Hill, Victoria Catterson, Erin Riordan and Grace Davison.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Victoria_station\", \"score\": 0.4322723513366671, \"rank\": 0.8227712953538799, \"text\": \"Victoria\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Victoria_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Victoria_station\"}, {\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin\", \"score\": 0.9909605893238411, \"rank\": 0.008928779362616157, \"text\": \"Erin\", \"types\": [\"Q82799\", \"Q202444\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin\"}, {\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Davison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grace Davison\", \"types\": [